{
  "text": "Within a VRML-enabled web browser 2 , the incident commander can rotate, pan and zoom the 3D models to navigate through streets and around buildings to gather information and search for victims. Figure 4 (middle) shows the 3D reconstructed model of the image still using a commercial version of Facade [CITATION_1] called Canoma.",
  "correct_citation": {
